    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，客户端这边您说的是两个WorkerNode吗？C1和C3？然后C2是Redis缓存，C4是IngressController？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
