    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，C1和C3都是WorkerNode，不过C1是主要负责对外连接的，C3是处理返回数据的。C2是Redis缓存做中间层，C4是IngressController做入口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C3",
        "C2",
        "C4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，客户端子图已经画好了。Vite层这边您提到有个Etcd集群，我记为P1？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Vite",
        "P1",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，P1是Vite层的Etcd集群。然后服务器端比较复杂，有S1到S5五个节点。S1、S3、S4都是EtcdCluster，S2是RedisCache，S5是WorkerNode。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Servidor",
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "服务器端三个Etcd集群？S1、S3、S4都是？那S2是Redis，S5是WorkerNode。这个结构我确认了，接下来画连接关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S2",
        "S5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，连接关系是这样的：C1连到C2，C2连到P1，P1再连到S1。这是主链路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "P1",
        "S1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "主链路画好了：C1--C2--P1--S1。然后服务器内部呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "P1",
        "S1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "服务器内部S1连S2，S2连S3，S3连S5。然后S2还要分叉连到S4，S4再连到S5。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5"
