      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：S1--S2--S3--S5是一条线，然后S2--S4--S5是另一条分支，最后都汇聚到S5？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，S5是服务器端的出口节点。然后S5要连回客户端的C3，这个返回链路很重要，数据格式是JSON，包含控制台信息、错误信息、符号表和AST。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S5",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，S5到C3的返回链路我标注上JSON数据格式。然后C3还要连到C4？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S5",
        "C3",
        "C4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，C3处理完数据后交给C4，也就是IngressController，最终返回给外部。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C3",
        "C4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "整体结构我画完了，但我发现C3和C1都是WorkerNode，都在Cliente子图里，但C1是入口方向，C3是出口方向，这样设计对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
