      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，这是双向分离的设计，C1专门接收请求，C3专门处理响应，避免单点瓶颈。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我检查一下连接关系。您说的S2--S4--S5这条分支，我之前画成了S3连S4，需要改成S2连S4。",
      "elements_involved": [
